data.description: This beautiful 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath home is located in Lake Highland Pointe, just a few steps away from R.T. Hill Middle school, highly ranked Hexter Elementary School and 1 mile away from White Rock Lake. Relax from your city life hustle and bustle in this one of a kind, low maintenance back yard. This home features a great floor plan with a large owner's bedroom downstairs. Owners just installed double pane Pella windows and radiant barrier in the attic. Oversized cul-de-sac provides lots of extra parking for your guests.
